Package: mp3-archive
Version: 1.0.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17)
Maintainer: musiren
Homepage: https://github.com/musiren/mp3-archive
Description: MP3 Archive Manager
 Audio file metadata manager that recursively scans directories,
 stores metadata in a SQLite database, and provides a PyQt6 GUI
 for searching, tagging, and playing your music library.
 .
 Supports MP3, FLAC, OGG, WAV, M4A, WMA, and Opus formats.
 Tag lookup via MusicBrainz and iTunes Search API.
